data.description: Step into luxury with this exceptional Colonial home nestled at the end of a peaceful cul-de-sac. The moment you enter through the French front doors, you'll be captivated by the attention to detail and quality finishes throughout.The tile floors throughout the home are a true marvel, combining style and functionality for a lasting impression. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece that will undoubtedly impress even the most discerning buyer. Modern and stylish,  appliances and finishes. The kitchen seamlessly flows into a spacious family room with a fireplace, creating the perfect setting for relaxation and gatherings. Enjoy outdoor living with an eating area featuring sliders that lead to a charming paver patio--a great space for entertaining friends and family. The home boasts both formal dining and living rooms, offering versatile spaces for entertaining or quiet moments. The pantry has been transformed into a wine bar, adding a touch of sophistication to your entertaining endeavors.The oversized master bedroom features a walk-in closet and a spa-like bath, creating a retreat within your own home.Three additional large bedrooms provide ample space for family and guests, accompanied by a full hall bath. The large partially walk-out finished basement is a versatile space, heated for year-round comfort and entertainment. A two-car garage, circular driveway, and no HOA provide convenience and flexibility.Close to commuting routes. Proximity to shopping, hospitals, and outletsThis is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Don't miss your opportunity to make this out
